  "excerpt": "Ever since I can remember, I have been obsessed with hand writing. Though I never thought mine was all that great growing up, I loved practicing and trying different ways to improve my lettering style. One of my fondest memories…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/2017/1/7/creative-lettering-for-kids",
  "legacyFile": "blog__2017__1__7__creative-lettering-for-kids.html",
  "imageCount": 3,
  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837180452-706D8VV6O243MSJVDQ5Q/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Ever since I can remember, I have been obsessed with hand writing. Though I never thought mine was all that great growing up, I loved practicing and trying different ways to improve my lettering style. One of my fondest memories includes passing colorful notes and notebooks to my friends in grade school and junior high. Arts &amp; crafts have played a key role in my early years and it is a dream come true to be able to work in an industry that values creativity. All the colorful markers and pen options out there still get me excited to this day. When I was asked by Jenny Doh to be a contributor to <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2j2oRlt\">Creative Lettering for Kids</a>, I gladly said yes! It is really cool to be a part of such a talented group - I don't feel worthy! </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837210145-GQG68U9T96YQ9H4MMZX6/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595837229488-84D7YNIX5RV75YYGDFTI/3c-Creativity%2Bquote%2Bby%2BBrene%2BBrown.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This piece didn't make it into the book, but I'm excited for you to see the ones that did. <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2j2oRlt\">Creative Lettering for Kids</a> is, in my opinion, great for all ages. Let's face it, we are really all kids at heart, right?! As I continue to strive to limit my time in front of digital devices, I feel even more inspired to try my hand at these awesome ideas. I have a feeling you will like them too!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}